text: Sterneck is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Esta Sterneck, German molecular biologist * Maximilian Daublebsky von Sterneck (1829–1897), Austrian admiral * Moritz Daublebsky-Sterneck (1912–1986), Austrian Righteous Among the Nations * Robert von Sterneck (1839–1910), Austro-Hungarian army officer, astronomer, and geodesist == See also == * Cape Sterneck * Sterneck Island
